data.description: OFFERS DUE SUNDAY, 4/28 AT 12PM. Adorable little snacc of a townhome in the Cedar Walk community of Ballantyne! This end unit is flooded with light throughout the day that helps showcase new LVP floors ('23), new paint throughout ('24) & tasteful fixtures. The well appointed spaces throughout continue as you move upstairs towards the dual primary setup. Both bedrooms have an ensuite bathroom and sizable closets. Outside have your own, picket fenced yard that connects to your garage! All within the Ardrey Kell school district and 5 minutes to Blakeney!
